  "name": "Deploy - Shopify Click & Collect",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-shopify-click-collect\">Deploy - Shopify Click &amp; Collect</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy a Shopify Click and Collect licence once a signed contract has been received:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Enable Shopify Click and Collect Feature in MGMT</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (55).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powffEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to <a href=\"\">MGMT</a></p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Shopify &gt; Shopify Site List</strong></p>\n<p>3. Filter by company name in <strong>Admin Link</strong></p>\n<p>4. Click on <span><strong>Edit</strong></span> and ensure that <strong>Click and Collect </strong>is ticked</p>\n<p>5. Select<strong> <span>Update</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Enable Shopify Click and Collect Feature in Retail Express db</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (56).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfpEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to client site eg. xxx.retailexpress.com.au</p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Settings &gt; Global Settings</strong></p>\n<p>3. Under section heading <strong>8. Web Store</strong> Ensure that Click and Collect Enabled is ticked<strong> </strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (57).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfuEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img>4. Select <strong><u>Save Changes</u></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Implementation &gt; Shopify Click &amp; Collect: Getting Started</strong></p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as Solved</p>",
